What is TBS Authoring work?
Involves creating step-by-step explanatory answers to specified questions strictly in-line with predefined authoring guidelines (*.docx format only).
Share your topics of your interest / specialization, Get the questions, Provide Solutions, Get Paid for every correct answer, just like Q&A payments.
You do not have to wait for questions; they are allocated to you by the team.
You can solve a question in multiple sittings, no limit of 2 hours per question.
Work as per predefined deadlines.
Any technical issues can also be emailed to eas_support@chegg.com

